Class GuidanceStreetLabelPresenter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.msdkui.guidance.base.BaseGuidancePresenter
      • com.here.msdkui.guidance.GuidanceStreetLabelPresenter

  • public class GuidanceStreetLabelPresenter
extends BaseGuidancePresenter
    Class that creates GuidanceStreetLabelData objects on maneuver update and feds them into registered listeners (e.g. GuidanceStreetLabelView.
